        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "I think your papa might have let you stay up a little longer; but he has promised that tonight-as we are to have the Christmas tree, and ever so much will be going on-you shall stay up till half past nine, if you like.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
