        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "She had an eager and growing thirst for knowledge, and was an apt scholar, whom any one with the least love for the profession might have delighted in teaching; and mr Dinsmore, a thorough scholar himself, and loving knowledge for its own sake-loving also his little pupil with all a father's fond, yearning affection-delighted in his task.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "When Elsie left her father she found that the Carringtons had just arrived.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Here are some dissected maps, Mary,\" replied Elsie, opening a drawer; \"would you not like them?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"No, indeed, thank you; they are too much like lessons.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Here are blocks; will you build houses?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000021_000001",
