        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "So, Elsie having first set the little ones to building block houses, supplied Harry Carrington-an older brother of Lucy's-with a book, and two younger boys with dissected maps to arrange, the four girls sat down in a circle on the carpet and began their game.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
