        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000074_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Please don't ask me, Lucy,\" replied the little girl, blushing deeply. \"Papa always has a good reason for what he does, and he is just the dearest, kindest, and best father that ever anybody had.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000078_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000078_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "The motion was carried without a dissenting voice, and in a few moments they all set out, a very merry party, full of fun and frolic.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000078_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000078_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "They had a very pleasant time, and returned barely in season to be dressed for dinner.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000079_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000079_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "They dined by themselves in the nursery, but were afterward taken down to the drawing room.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000083_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000083_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Ah!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000083_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000083_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "Well, I like to see it; blushes are very becoming.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000083_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000083_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "mr Dinsmore\"--to Elsie's papa, who just then came toward them-\"you ought to be very proud of this child; she is the very image of yourself, and a perfect little beauty, too.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000090_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000090_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"No, papa,\" she said, \"I do not mind, when people say such things, because I know the Bible says, 'Favor is deceitful, and beauty is vain;' and in another place, 'He that flattereth his neighbor spreadeth a net for his feet.' So I will try to keep away from that lady; shall I not, papa?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000092_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000092_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "There was lurking within his breast a vague consciousness that her father needed such a safeguard, but had it not.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000093_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000093_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "Lucy, who was standing at the window, turned quickly round.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000094_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000094_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Come, girls,\" she said, \"let us run out and see them off; they're bringing up the horses.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000094_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000094_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "And see, there's Miss Adelaide in her riding dress and cap; how pretty she looks!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000102_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000102_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"I wish you were, my pet; I always love to have you with me; but you know it wouldn't do; you have your little guests to entertain.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000102_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000102_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "Good by, darling.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000106_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000106_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "But at length tea being over, and all, both old and young, assembled as if by common consent in the drawing room, it began to be whispered about that their curiosity was now on the point of being gratified.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000108_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000108_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "A large Christmas tree had been set up at the further end of the room, and, with its myriad of lighted tapers, and its load of toys and bonbons, interspersed with many a richer and more costly gift, made quite a display.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000109_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000109_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Beautiful! beautiful!\" cried the children, clapping their hands and dancing about with delight, while their elders, perhaps equally pleased, expressed their admiration after a more staid and sober fashion.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000113_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000113_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"From your papa,\" she said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000113_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000113_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Go and thank him: it is well worth it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000126_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000126_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "It was only a gold pencil.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000129_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000129_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Keep it in your pocket, and use it every day, won't you, papa?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000130_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000130_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Yes, my pet, I will; but I thought you said you had no present for me?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000134_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000134_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "He put it in her hand, and ran away again.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000134_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000134_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "Elsie looked up in her father's face inquiringly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000137_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000137_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"No, dearest,\" he said; \"for though I, too, am fond of sweet things, I will not eat them while I refuse them to you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000138_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000138_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Do, papa,\" she urged, \"it would give me pleasure to see you enjoying it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000142_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000142_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"Is it half past nine already, papa?\" she asked.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3440_171009_000143_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3440/171009/3440_171009_000143_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3440",
        "content": "\"It is ten, my dear child, and high time you were in bed,\" he said, smiling at her look of astonishment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]